OL,3,CWoman, 31, left in hospital corridor
OL,4,Cfor hours at 'most vulnerable' `
OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,FThe family of a 31-year-old woman said
OL,8,Fshe was "abandoned" in a hospital
OL,9,Fcorridor for hours before her death,
OL,10,Fan inquest has heard.
OL,12,FTamara Davis was said to be in her
OL,13,F"most vulnerable moments" when she was
OL,14,Fleft on a trolley in a hallway at
OL,15,FRoyal Sussex County Hospital for
OL,16,Faround 10 hours.
OL,18,FShe died of multiple organ failure and
OL,19,Fsepsis caused by influenza on December
OL,20,F13, 2022.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
