OL,3,CWoman, 31, left in hospital corridor
OL,4,Cfor hours at 'most vulnerable' `
OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,FHowever the coroner expressed her
OL,8,F"substantial concern" over the use of
OL,9,Fcorridors and said she would be
OL,10,Fwriting to Department of Health and
OL,11,FNHS England over the ongoing problem
OL,12,Fin a prevention of future deaths
OL,13,Freport.
OL,15,FThe inquest heard that Ms Davis'
OL,16,Fpartner Raphael Ifill had rushed her
OL,17,Fto hospital on December 10, after she
OL,18,Fhad what was thought to be a bad cold
OL,19,Ffor several days, before collapsing at
OL,20,Fhome.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
