OL,3,CWoman, 31, left in hospital corridor
OL,4,Cfor hours at 'most vulnerable' `
OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,F"That is a tragedy," he said.
OL,9,FHe added it was a response to
OL,10,F"overwhelming pressure on the system".
OL,12,FThe inquest heard that Ms Davis was in
OL,13,Fa resuscitation room until 5.30am on
OL,14,FDecember 11, when she was then moved
OL,15,Fto the corridor where up to 20
OL,16,Fpatients stayed throughout the day.
OL,18,FShe was given one dose of antibiotics,
OL,19,Ffluids and paracetamol during her
OL,20,Ftreatment, and was moved out of the
OL,21,Fcorridor to another cubicle at 3.20pm.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
