OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,FThe inquest heard how her condition
OL,8,Fdeteriorated and she was moved into
OL,9,Fintensive care later in the night on
OL,10,FDecember 11 before she died on the
OL,11,Fmorning of December 13.
OL,13,FDr Leonard said he had many "sleepless
OL,14,Fnights" over what happened to Ms Davis
OL,15,Fbut added: "I still do not think we
OL,16,Fcould have predicted what would happen
OL,17,Fto her."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
