OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,FHe said he believed Ms Davis had
OL,8,Finfluenza and sepsis caused by the flu
OL,9,Fstrain, which saw 10,000 hospital
OL,10,Fadmissions during the 2022/23 flu
OL,11,Fseason that year where the "majority"
OL,12,Fof young patients recovered in two to
OL,13,Fthree days.
OL,15,FWhile Ms Davis was "diagnosable" with
OL,16,Fsepsis at 4.24pm on December 11, she
OL,17,Fwas not screened for the life-
OL,18,Fthreatening condition until two hours
OL,19,Flater, the inquest heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
