OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,FHowever Dr Leonard said he was not
OL,8,Fsure it would have made "any material
OL,9,Fdifference to the outcome" if she was
OL,10,Fdiagnosed earlier.
OL,12,FThe inquest also heard from senior
OL,13,Fsister Alice Edmondson who was on
OL,14,Fshift that day and asked for Ms Davis
OL,15,Fto be moved out of the corridor.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
