OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,F"I really want the family to know that
OL,8,FI, as a senior nurse, I feel upset
OL,9,Feveryday I go to work that people are
OL,10,Fin the corridor."
OL,12,FThe inquest heard that having no
OL,13,Fpatients in a corridor was a priority
OL,14,Ffor the trust, which runs the Brighton
OL,15,Fhospital.
OL,17,FFollowing the conclusion, Mr Ifill
OL,18,Fsaid the hospital "could have done
OL,19,Fmore" and the duty of care was
OL,20,F"absolutely shocking".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
