OL,7,F"We shouldn't be changing bed sheets,
OL,8,Fwe shouldn't be carrying her to the
OL,9,Ftoilet," he said.
OL,11,F"She felt abandoned. She felt alone,"
OL,12,Fhe said.
OL,14,F"If I fall sick in Brighton I've got
OL,15,Fno faith to go to that hospital. It
OL,16,Fjust feels really bad in there."
