OL,7,FChief Nurse at The University
OL,8,FHospitals Sussex NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,9,FMaggie Davies said: "We wish to extend
OL,10,Four heartfelt condolences to Miss
OL,11,FDavis' family and friends.
OL,13,F"We entirely accept that the
OL,14,Fexperience Tamara, and her family, had
OL,15,Fin the ED corridor before admission to
OL,16,Fintensive care fell short of the
OL,17,Fstandards our patients and families
OL,18,Fshould expect ` that is a matter of
OL,19,Fdeep regret, and we are truly sorry.
